WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.525
Python sizning kodingizda muammoga duch kelganda,

00:00:02.525 --> 00:00:06.965
Muammo yuz berganda u qaysi qatorda ishlaganligini sizga aytib beradi.

00:00:06.965 --> 00:00:08.565
Ushbu kodda,

00:00:08.565 --> 00:00:11.200
birinchi muammo ikkinchi chiziqda ko‘rinadi.

00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:14.830
Endi o‘z-o‘zidan, ushbu kod satri juda yaxshi ko‘rinadi.

00:00:14.830 --> 00:00:18.980
Oldingi singari kod qatorlarini ko‘rdik va ular ishladilar.

00:00:18.980 --> 00:00:21.660
turtle lar rangini sariq rangga bo‘yashga muvaffaq bo‘ldik,

00:00:21.660 --> 00:00:23.625
yoki yashil, yoki biz xohlagan boshqa rangga.

00:00:23.625 --> 00:00:27.420
Bu yerda nima bo‘lyapti? Nega endi bu muammo?

00:00:27.420 --> 00:00:31.100
Odatda, Python kodni yuqoridan pastga ishlaydi

00:00:31.100 --> 00:00:35.285
quyida siz bir qator ko‘rsatmalarni bajarishingiz kerak.

00:00:35.285 --> 00:00:37.370
Avval kompyuter birinchi qatorda ishlaydi,

00:00:37.370 --> 00:00:39.580
keyin ikkinchi qator va hokazo.

00:00:39.580 --> 00:00:43.835
Ammo, bu ko‘rsatmalar to‘g‘ri tartibda bo‘lishi kerakligini anglatadi.

00:00:43.835 --> 00:00:45.410
Agar ular noto‘g‘ri tartibda bo‘lsa,

00:00:45.410 --> 00:00:47.450
kompyuter, ehtimol, yo‘lni yo‘qatib qoladi,

00:00:47.450 --> 00:00:49.380
va bu yerda shunday holat sodir bo‘lgan.

00:00:49.380 --> 00:00:53.115
Ushbu dasturning dastlabki uchta qatorini yana bir ko‘rib chiqing.

00:00:53.115 --> 00:00:58.335
Dastur ikkinchi qatorda biron narsa qilish uchun Melinda ismli turtle ni olishga harakat qilmoqda.

00:00:58.335 --> 00:01:03.505
Ammo biz uchinchi qatorga qadar Melinda nomli turtle ni yaratamiz deb aytmaymiz.

00:01:03.505 --> 00:01:08.665
Dastur Melinda ismli turtle bo‘lmaganligi, unga nima qilish kerakligini aytolmaydi.

00:01:08.665 --> 00:01:11.335
Xato xabari - ism xatosi

00:01:11.335 --> 00:01:14.270
har doim kod biron bir ob’ektga tegishli bo‘lmagan nomga 

00:01:14.270 --> 00:01:17.905
murojaat qilishini anglatadi.

00:01:17.905 --> 00:01:21.320
Xatoning qolgan qismi sizga ism, 

00:01:21.320 --> 00:01:25.155
xatoning koddagi qatori haqida xabar beradi.

00:01:25.155 --> 00:01:30.875
Shunday qilib, ushbu xatoni tuzatish uchun biz qilishimiz kerak bo‘lgan narsa bu ikki qatorni to‘g‘ri tartibda qo‘yishdir.

00:01:30.875 --> 00:01:33.645
Buni qilganimizdan so‘ng, kod ishlay boshlaydi,

00:01:33.645 --> 00:01:36.755
hech bo‘lmaganda keyingi xato yuz bermaguncha.

00:01:36.755 --> 00:01:40.080
Buni tuzatib ko‘ring.

